---
title: Asian-Style Crumbed Chicken Salad with Creamy Japanese Dressing
description: There’s nothing quite like the golden crust of a good old-fashioned crumbed chicken to cheer you up – that’s just
simple science. And as for condiments? We think the delish and creamy Japanese dressing might just make for
the ultimate finishing touch in this speedy lunch delight.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*
